      }, {
        "html" : "<p><img style=\"float: right;\" src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/tcdn.mobidonia.com/codecanyon/info/Screenshot+at+Mar+20+23-01-48.png\" alt=\"TinyMCE\" width=\"415\" height=\"154\" /></p> <div class=\"col-md-12\">  <h2>How to use the Scanner app</h2> <p>The scanning app provides an easy way for venues and promoters to scan tickets at events without the need for any additional hardware!&nbsp;</p> <h3>Here is step by step how to use the Scanner App</h3> </div>   <br/>   <ol> <li>The costumer should open the order that will be scanned.&nbsp;Scan the order&nbsp; by placing the device&nbsp; of the costumer&nbsp; under the phone's camera. The&nbsp; QR code&nbsp; will be&nbsp; scanned&nbsp;automatically.<br /><br /><img style=\"display: block;     margin-left: auto;     margin-right: auto;     width: 50%;\" src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/universalapp-a272a.appspot.com/o/39018472_188393191913468_417050803434422272_n.jpg?alt=media&amp;token=83de644d-7a43-4235-a582-329fff0d911d\" alt=\"TinyMCE\" width=\"165\" height=\"295\" /><br /><br /></li> <li>After the successful scan it will be displayed the order details. And if the order is doesn't used yet, you will see the button to the bottom <strong>\"Use the ticket\".</strong><br /><img style=\"display: block;     margin-left: auto;     margin-right: auto;     width: 50%;\" src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/universalapp-a272a.appspot.com/o/39200812_1757158060998131_1709184859668217856_n.jpg?alt=media&amp;token=5bfa7c97-6555-4f3c-95ae-b9d55a90802e\" alt=\"\" width=\"167\" height=\"297\" /><br /><br /><br /></li> <li>Now, to use the order just click on the button to use the ticket. And then should display alert that says that <strong>\"Now the ticket is used\".<br /><br /><img style=\"display: block;     margin-left: auto;     margin-right: auto;     width: 50%;\" src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/universalapp-a272a.appspot.com/o/39329270_313056232589075_2817584265133293568_n.jpg?alt=media&amp;token=fd338c93-7d8e-4df0-a3cf-69e8d7ca8be9\" alt=\"\" width=\"169\" height=\"300\" /><br /><br /></strong></li> <li>Now because&nbsp;the ticket is used, you should see that&nbsp; ticket is already used.<br /><br /><img style=\"display: block;     margin-left: auto;     margin-right: auto;     width: 50%;\" src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/universalapp-a272a.appspot.com/o/39080839_512965399164905_4965479615813386240_n.jpg?alt=media&amp;token=fc649bfd-1d8c-468f-a042-b10507f0c4fd\" alt=\"\" width=\"169\" height=\"300\" /><br /><br /><strong>NOTE:&nbsp;</strong>If you click on the button it should display alert that says that <strong>\"Ticket is already used\"</strong><br /><br /><br /><img style=\"display: block;     margin-left: auto;     margin-right: auto;     width: 50%;\" src=\"https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/universalapp-a272a.appspot.com/o/39109068_247040505942417_2480103310019788800_n.jpg?alt=media&amp;token=87cad1e7-4d24-4a8b-a55f-e5ff50480951\" alt=\"\" width=\"172\" height=\"306\" /><br /><br /> <h3>So that is it. We are hoping that you will enjoying using our app.</h3> &nbsp;&nbsp;<br /><br /></li> </ol>",
